### Upload XLSX → PDF
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/xlsx-to-pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ../fixtures/sample.xlsx
--boundary--

### Poll task status
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}

### Download result
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}/download
